."],[9088,9217,"There are only two women in my life."],[9217,9259,"That's you,"],[9259,9346,"and that's my mom."],[9346,9430,"My dad died"],[9430,9522,"and she raised me on my own,"],[9522,9697,"after you saved me from that car wreck."],[9697,9851,"Why would I ever want to betray that?"],[9851,10018,"Don't drag your mom into this."],[10043,10168,"And don't play the victim."],[10285,10393,"You want proof?"],[10393,10489,"Fine!"],[10489,10614,"Your other woman,"],[10614,10789,"I caught her in the act."],[10894,10927,"Wait."],[10944,10985,"Caught who?"],[10985,11086,"What proof?"]],"14":[[79,125,"I don't know what"],[125,187,"you're talking about."],[187,229,"You, but"],[229,312,"you must have"],[312,408,"the wrong person here."],[408,579,"Oh, the wrong person."],[579,746,"You're still playing dumb?"],[746,892,"Everyone here saw it."],[930,1013,"Look, son."],[1051,1142,"Just admit it."],[1188,1305,"It's one of those mistakes"],[1305,1443,"all men make."],[1493,1580,"Own up to it."],[1597,1743,"Apologize and move on."],[1822,1951,"No need to drag this out."],[2014,2060,"Listen Sir,"],[2072,2127,"I'm trying to..."],[2135,2385,"Apologize to Mia."],[2427,2648,"Save yourself the headache."],[2652,2690,"Listen,"],[2690,2773,"I'm not going to apologize"],[2773,2815,"for something"],[2815,3015,"that I haven't even done."],[3015,3128,"You told me"],[3128,3174,"I was"],[3174,3265,"the only woman"],[3265,3407,"you've ever loved."],[3474,3591,"I'm such a fool."],[3749,3870,"I shouldn't have saved you"],[3870,3962,"that day."],[3962,4116,"Don't rewrite history, Mia."],[4170,4266,"If you have proof,"],[4283,4366,"show it."],[4458,4633,"You want proof?"],[4988,5084,"Here."],[5121,5296,"Here's that pearl bracelet"],[5296,5497,"you gave that whore."],[5530,5576,"What?"],[5588,5693,"Pearl bracelet?"],[5693,5759,"I never even bought"],[5759,5847,"one of these before."],[5880,5939,"Don't pretend"],[5939,6039,"like you don't know."],[6039,6147,"That is not just some cheap"],[6147,6268,"trinket that you find"],[6268,6393,"at a mall kiosk."],[6393,6493,"A bracelet like that"],[6493,6535,"is worth"],[6535,6694,"hundreds of thousands."],[6694,6735,"You can't"],[6735,6835,"just exactly give"],[6835,6952,"that away by accident."],[7002,7107,"This can't be right."],[7107,7178,"A piece like this"],[7178,7319,"isn't just expensive."],[7319,7399,"It's unique."],[7399,7428,"The only one"],[7428,7524,"I’ve ever seen like it"],[7524,7724,"belonged to my mother."],[7766,7874,"Where did you get this from?"]],"15":[[12,208,"From your mistress!"],[262,437,"Our family is not"],[437,588,"wealthy like yours."],[588,658,"But that doesn't"],[658,721,"give you the right"],[721,921,"to humiliate me like this!"],[975,1176,"I've given you my heart,"],[1184,1263,"my loyalty."],[1263,1422,"And this is how you repay me?"],[1422,1584,"Enough, Mia!"],[1584,1680,"Stop making a spectacle"],[1680,1801,"in front of everyone."],[1801,1872,"You making up lies,"],[1885,2022,"dragging us through the mud."],[2022,2106,"Is this your end game"],[2106,2306,"to just ruin the wedding?"],[3228,3294,"Don't even think"],[3294,3445,"about escaping."],[3445,3595,"Noah!"],[3712,3849,"Shut up!"],[3849,3916,"You think your precious"],[3916,4041,"Noah Harper’s going to save you?"],[4483,4683,"What is so special"],[4708,4854,"about that Harper brat?"],[4892,4979,"That you two"],[5013,5263,"are both so eager to sleep with him?"],[5638,5776,"Maybe"],[5776,5922,"I should leave you"],[5922,6089,"something memorable."],[6089,6231,"Let’s see if Harper"],[6231,6431,"recognizes you after this."],[7119,7182,"What was that?"]],"16":[[41,241,"Oh, that..."],[312,513,"That was..."],[517,625,"that was just a"],[625,729,"clueless relative,"],[796,875,"of ours..."],[921,975,"who thought it would be"],[975,1059,"fun to bring their dog."],[1176,1326,"So we locked it in the back."],[1376,1405,"Right?"],[1463,1580,"Enough of this nonsense."],[1597,1714,"Today is a very"],[1714,1851,"important day."],[1851,1943,"Let's get this wedding"],[1943,2035,"back on track"],[2035,2114,"and throw"],[2114,2189,"all this mistress"],[2189,2406,"business aside until later."],[2423,2473,"Okay?"],[2548,2681,"Mia, don’t ruin everything"],[2715,2815,"Noah's gonna leave."],[2944,3028,"Noah,"],[3061,3169,"She's just all worked up"],[3169,3253,"because she"],[3253,3361,"loves you so much!"],[3453,3536,"My mom should be here"],[3536,3616,"by now."],[3616,3687,"Yeah,"],[3724,3841,"I can’t wait for her"],[3841,3908,"to get here"],[3908,3995,"so she can clear up"],[3995,4141,"this mess for me."],[4141,4266,"Really, Mia?"],[4266,4366,"You sound ridiculous."],[4366,4554,"I don't care, Noah."],[4554,4692,"I deserve an explanation"],[4692,4842,"and I'm getting it today!"],[5159,5226,"This?"],[5342,5526,"This blueprint,"],[5526,5726,"it's from the Elysium Estate."],[5747,5818,"You gave this"],[5818,5960,"to your mistress, didn't you?"],[6585,6694,"This is the first blueprint"],[6694,6894,"that I ever designed."],[6940,7015,"How did this get here?"]],"17":[[120,260,"How did this get here?"],[260,433,"I asked you for a mansion,"],[433,530,"and instead you're giving"],[530,626,"a multimillion-dollar"],[626,760,"estate to some other woman?"],[760,913,"I never gave it to anyone!"],[1056,1260,"Sir, that estate has been"],[1260,1400,"abandoned for years."],[1400,1446,"Your mother is"],[1446,1510,"the one that kept it"],[1510,1643,"under her care."],[1690,1813,"Ms. Stone,"],[1813,1910,"this is for sure a"],[1910,2023,"misunderstanding."],[2023,2130,"Oh,"],[2130,2260,"you want me to believe"],[2260,2303,"that this is a"],[2303,2420,"misunderstanding?"],[2420,2620,"Do you think I'm stupid?"],[2710,2786,"Listen, my mom handles"],[2786,2916,"all my property."],[2916,2973,"I have not given"],[2973,3136,"anything to anyone."],[3136,3336,"Don't lie to me, Noah."],[3386,3513,"Whether it's the estate"],[3513,3636,"or the bracelet,"],[3636,3703,"I don't care"],[3703,3786,"if they're not mine."],[3786,3916,"But you sure as hell better"],[3916,4000,"not be giving them"],[4000,4080,"to anyone else."],[4106,4146,"Fine."],[4190,4293,"You don't believe me?"],[4293,4376,"Let's call my mom."],[4376,4466,"She'll clear everything up."],[7086,7220,"Your call has been forwarded"],[7220,7303,"to an automatic"],[7303,7426,"voice message system."]],"18":[[33,216,"My darling?"],[216,379,"First “son.”"],[379,575,"Now, “darling?”"],[588,754,"Lady,"],[754,955,"You're full of surprises."],[1034,1217,"She’s not answering."],[1217,1297,"Have someone go check her"],[1297,1497,"hotel room."],[2652,2706,"You really thought"],[2706,2907,"you could get away,"],[2973,3174,"If she was here we would see her by now."],[3211,3370,"Let's check outside."],[3370,3407,"I'll send people"],[3407,3503,"to check the entire city"],[3503,3703,"if we have to."],[5605,5801,"Where is she?"],[5801,5885,"Where is the woman"],[5885,5972,"in this picture?"]],"19":[[25,87,"Oh!"],[133,258,"You didn't know your little"],[258,458,"homewrecker was married?"],[475,675,"I'm going to ask you again."],[717,846,"Where is she?"],[846,955,"You're losing it over"],[955,1042,"a homewrecker."],[1042,1226,"Seriously?"],[1226,1305,"I'm going to ask you"],[1305,1434,"one more time."],[1434,1634,"Where is she?"],[1659,1860,"Noah, I..."],[1868,2072,"Oh, help me!"],[3841,4041,"Mom!"],[4045,4083,"Mom!"]],"20":[[104,158,"Let her go,"],[158,254,"you son of bitch!"],[1213,1393,"Okay, mom, it’s me."],[1443,1480,"I’m sorry"],[1480,1651,"I wasn’t here sooner."],[2085,2127,"Son,"],[2127,2260,"you finally came!"],[3040,3240,"I'm going to make them pay for this."]],"21":[[387,504,"I need a doctor now!"],[775,975,"Yes, sir."],[1835,2002,"Noah, are you serious?"],[2002,2143,"You're Mia's fiancé,"],[2143,2268,"and you have the nerve"],[2268,2348,"to walk out of here"],[2348,2439,"with that woman"],[2439,2640,"in front of everyone?"],[2815,2923,"Noah,"],[2923,3086,"what do I even mean to you?"],[3086,3178,"After everything"],[3178,3286,"we've been through."],[3286,3374,"You'd rather"],[3374,3574,"choose her over me?"],[3582,3707,"Can you believe it?"],[3707,3807,"The great Harper heir"],[3807,3858,"turns out to be"],[3858,4012,"nothing but a lying cheater."],[4012,4137,"This is crazy."],[4137,4229,"If I were you, Mia,"],[4229,4429,"I would walk out right now!"],[4487,4688,"She's not my mistress."],[4754,4854,"She's my mother."]],"22":[[37,237,"She's actually Noah's mother?"],[246,446,"My future mother in law?"],[462,546,"Oh, God."],[546,646,"It's over."],[646,880,"I'm done for."],[884,930,"Anyone else"],[930,1130,"have any more questions?"],[1159,1359,"Because I have one."],[1359,1484,"Who did this?"],[1484,1685,"Who hurt my mother?"],[2281,2481,"Nobody?"],[2519,2719,"Ryan!"],[2969,3169,"So, I'll ask again."],[3253,3336,"Who broke"],[3336,3528,"my mother's necklace?"],[3528,3728,"Who hit her?"],[3820,3912,"Who else other than this"],[3912,4012,"piece of shit?"],[4012,4212,"Laid hands on my mother."],[4245,4279,"Noah."],[4279,4333,"We didn't know"],[4333,4533,"she was your mother."],[4554,4662,"It was you,"],[4662,4779,"wasn’t it?"]],"23":[[62,262,"I didn’t know..."],[266,312,"Didn’t know?"],[400,446,"You know that"],[446,571,"she's the last person I have"],[571,742,"on this earth."],[742,875,"You didn't know"],[875,1055,"that without her,"],[1055,1255,"I wouldn't even be here today?"],[1343,1426,"A lesser man would take"],[1426,1626,"his anger out on you."],[1760,1960,"But I'm not going to do that."],[2118,2164,"It's on you"],[2164,2360,"for raising her to be like this."],[2377,2439,"I really"],[2439,2560,"I really didn't know."],[2560,2761,"You didn't know?"],[2761,2823,"If she wasn't"],[2823,2927,"someone “important”"],[2927,3019,"that make it right,"],[3019,3078,"that you treated her"],[3078,3199,"like trash?"],[3199,3307,"Noah, I'm so sorry."],[3307,3357,"Please."],[3357,3470,"I only acted that way"],[3470,3603,"because of those photos."],[3603,3699,"I misunderstood."],[3699,3762,"I thought she was"],[3762,3828,"your mistress."],[3828,3974,"Oh, misunderstood?"],[3974,4045,"That's the best you've got"],[4045,4216,"that you misunderstood."],[4216,4304,"This is just a"],[4304,4425,"misunderstanding."],[4425,4525,"A misunderstanding"],[4525,4650,"within the family."],[4650,4758,"Family?"],[4758,4859,"No, she's not"],[4859,5009,"part of the Harper family."],[5009,5209,"Oh, don't say that."],[5242,5430,"Mia saved your life."],[5430,5563,"Yes, she saved my life."],[5563,5613,"Because of that,"],[5613,5689,"I've indulged"],[5689,5772,"every little demand"],[5772,5826,"that you people"],[5826,5876,"have thrown at me."],[5876,6068,"But hitting my mother?"],[6068,6160,"You know that..."],[6160,6264,"That crosses the line."],[6435,6519,"You better pray"],[6519,6648,"she's all right."],[6648,6773,"If she's not,"],[6773,6923,"I’m gonna make sure everybody"],[6923,7048,"wishes that they were dead."]],"24":[[25,225,"We just came here for a show,"],[342,542,"not to be involved."],[846,1030,"We already apologized."],[1030,1230,"What more do you want?"],[1263,1405,"I didn't even do anything that bad to her"],[1405,1551,"anyway."],[1551,1626,"You think money makes"],[1626,1826,"you untouchable,"],[1868,2068,"look at him!"],[2068,2152,"Acting like he's"],[2152,2285,"better than us."],[2285,2485,"Just because he's rich."],[2631,2831,"You still don’t get it,"],[2831,2932,"don’t you?"],[2932,3098,"Whatever you did to my mom,"],[3098,3194,"I’ll pay it back"],[3194,3353,"a thousand times over."],[4350,4412,"Who's next?"]],"25":[[258,296,"Mia."],[316,429,"Mia, help me."],[554,688,"Don't forget you have my kid in there."],[688,754,"Please,"],[846,913,"save me."],[996,1067,"Or I'll tell everyone"],[1067,1222,"your dirty little secret."],[1380,1434,"Don’t!"],[1555,1597,"Noah,"],[1597,1651,"please!"],[1906,1968,"I'm begging you."],[1968,2068,"Please forgive me."],[2068,2168,"Forgive you?"],[2248,2448,"I will never forgive you."],[2515,2619,"You think my mom"],[2619,2819,"will ever forgive you?"],[2827,3028,"Vivian's nice."],[3040,3240,"She'll probably let it slide!"],[3307,3365,"Please, Noah."],[3365,3482,"Please, just give me..."],[3482,3682,"Just give me a chance."],[5100,5288,"I will never forgive you."]],"26":[[100,221,"I will never"],[221,279,"forgive you."],[387,446,"Mom, are you..."],[521,546,"okay?"],[546,592,"Did they"],[625,679,"take care of all"],[679,729,"your injuries?"],[729,759,"Or"],[813,863,"maybe you should"],[863,942,"just head home, mom."],[975,1167,"I can take care of this."],[1167,1247,"Anybody that hurt you"],[1247,1351,"is going to pay."],[1384,1509,"No, no."],[1509,1576,"This is something"],[1576,1772,"I need to handle myself."],[2485,2544,"Vivian,"],[2556,2623,"Vivian, I..."],[2665,2752,"I'm so sorry!"],[2752,2852,"It's my fault!"],[2852,2952,"Please forgive me!"],[3224,3403,"Really?"],[3403,3520,"Who said we were close"],[3520,3720,"enough for you to call me that?"],[3820,3883,"I didn't know"],[3883,4083,"you were Noah’s mom!"],[4083,4137,"I thought you"],[4137,4245,"were his mistress!"],[4245,4354,"I'm so sorry."],[4354,4441,"Please!"],[4441,4525,"I only did that"],[4525,4733,"because I love him so much."],[4825,4854,"Please,"],[4854,4929,"I'll do anything"],[4929,5038,"to make this right."],[5038,5134,"I'll do anything."],[5134,5301,"I'll treat you right."],[5301,5384,"I'll take care of you."],[5384,5455,"I'll even treat you"],[5455,5655,"like my own mother."],[5672,5822,"Please, I..."],[5851,5976,"I won't ever hurt you."],[5976,6156,"Please forgive me."],[6156,6264,"What about"],[6264,6348,"everything that happened"],[6348,6460,"to me today?"],[6460,6577,"Every slap,"],[6577,6769,"every humiliation."],[6769,6923,"Tell me, Mia,"],[6923,6994,"how are you going to"],[6994,7065,"make up for all that?"],[7182,7340,"If I had known that you were"],[7340,7432,"Noah’s mom,"],[7432,7632,"I wouldn't have dared."],[7632,7803,"Please forgive me, Vivian."],[7803,7949,"For Noah's sake, please!"],[8191,8287,"Vivian,"],[8287,8475,"I'm so sorry."],[8475,8550,"I was wrong!"],[8575,8625,"Here!"],[8633,8850,"Please hit me again if that's"],[8850,8896,"what's going to"],[8896,9067,"make things right."],[9067,9267,"If Noah hadn’t found me today,"],[9267,9346,"I probably wouldn’t have"],[9346,9442,"made it out alive."],[9488,9563,"I told you,"],[9563,9713,"I wasn’t a mistress,"],[9713,9909,"but you wouldn't listen."],[9909,10110,"You don’t deserve to marry Noah,"],[10168,10310,"and you have lost your chance"],[10310,10427,"of ever being a"],[10427,10535,"part of the Harper family."]],"27":[[58,120,"Do you really think"],[120,154,"that there's a future"],[154,354,"between us?"],[379,579,"We're done."],[650,721,"At one point,"],[721,913,"I was really grateful"],[913,980,"because you saved"],[980,1121,"Noah's life."],[1121,1242,"I even went out of my way"],[1242,1443,"to find you a special gift."],[1543,1626,"A gift?"],[1626,1672,"Yeah."],[1672,1718,"The keys"],[1718,1776,"to the mansion"],[1776,1947,"that you threw in the trash."],[1947,2014,"The bracelet"],[2014,2181,"that you smashed."],[2181,2369,"Those were for you."],[2369,2460,"It's too bad"],[2460,2615,"you destroyed them all."],[2615,2781,"What?"],[2940,3053,"Those were for me?"],[3319,3432,"It was their idea!"],[3432,3536,"They did it!"],[3536,3632,"I didn't do anything."],[3632,3816,"They set me up!"],[3816,3949,"Vivian, please."],[3949,4012,"Please, Vivian."],[4012,4212,"Give me another chance."],[4262,4379,"And maybe..."],[4379,4458,"Maybe"],[4458,4658,"another set of gifts, too."],[4692,4892,"Wow, wow, Mia."],[4904,5100,"You are unbelievable."],[5100,5301,"Let me make this clear."],[5309,5501,"Those gifts were mine."],[5501,5626,"They were only yours"],[5626,5739,"if I was going to give them"],[5739,5776,"to you."],[5776,5955,"Do you understand?"],[5955,6089,"Vivian, please."],[6335,6393,"You brought"],[6393,6594,"this on yourself."],[6606,6744,"That mansion?"],[6744,6894,"Noah designed it."],[6894,7019,"Someone once offered me"],[7019,7127,"a $300 million."],[7136,7269,"The bracelet?"],[7344,7545,"Priceless Harper family heirloom"],[7570,7770,"worth $2 million."],[7970,8170,"But that locket,"],[8191,8387,"that was the last photo"],[8437,8633,"of my husband."],[8637,8825,"Do you have any idea"],[8825,9025,"what you destroyed?"],[9163,9363,"So, tell me Mia."],[9388,9530,"How are you going to pay me back"],[9563,9722,"for all of these?"],[9722,9834,"Noah,"],[9834,9909,"all these years"],[9909,10043,"we've been together."],[10043,10243,"This is my last chance."],[10276,10393,"No."],[10393,10481,"We've been together"],[10481,10656,"for so long."],[10656,10823,"You can't do this to me,"],[10823,10965,"please."],[10965,11065,"I love you so much."],[11065,11265,"I've done so much for you."],[11327,11373,"Please."],[11373,11461,"Please, just give"],[11461,11586,"me one more chance."]],"28":[[0,120,"There is nothing"],[120,237,"left between us, Mia."],[333,442,"We're done."],[483,529,"Sir,"],[654,775,"here's the surveillance footage"],[788,900,"from the hotel"],[900,1017,"and banquet hall."],[1368,1451,"Get her in there!"],[1985,2039,"You did this"],[2039,2156,"to my mother?"],[2431,2569,"I can't believe that"],[2569,2602,"I was ever"],[2602,2802,"stupid enough to fall for you."],[2806,2861,"Just because you"],[2861,2919,"saved my life."],[2919,3003,"That is the only reason"],[3003,3203,"that you are not gone."],[3207,3365,"This wedding's off."],[3428,3503,"From now on,"],[3553,3737,"you are nothing to me"],[3737,3853,"and my family."],[3853,4029,"No, no, no, Noah."],[4120,4258,"Please don't call this off"],[4258,4437,"just because of your mother."],[4437,4612,"Yeah, Mia,"],[4612,4779,"she messed up."],[4779,4934,"You gotta give her a chance"],[4934,5025,"to fix it."],[5025,5080,"Mia,"],[5209,5422,"you will never, ever,"],[5543,5734,"be a part of the Harper family."],[5759,5822,"This wedding"],[5822,6022,"is officially canceled."],[6106,6189,"Take them out of here,"],[6189,6289,"and turn them over to the police."],[6456,6656,"No, wait!"],[6660,6752,"Wait!"],[6752,6881,"You can't call off the wedding."],[7015,7161,"I'm pregnant!"],[7161,7248,"It's Noah’s baby!"]],"29":[[58,183,"You're pregnant?"],[308,346,"Yea."],[483,571,"A baby?"],[767,813,"Noah,"],[813,1013,"you can't walk out on this."],[1021,1213,"There's a life at stake."],[1213,1338,"Yeah, and"],[1338,1409,"even if you don't"],[1409,1455,"get married,"],[1530,1643,"you can't ignore the kid."],[1643,1714,"I mean, think about what"],[1714,1818,"this will do to the Harper"],[1818,1964,"family's reputation."],[2118,2206,"Why didn't you tell me that"],[2206,2314,"you were pregnant?"],[2344,2494,"I have the pregnancy report"],[2494,2535,"right here."],[3165,3261,"Are you really going"],[3261,3461,"to deny your own baby?"],[3478,3566,"Please, Noah,"],[3566,3720,"it's legit."],[3799,3862,"Noah, please,"],[3862,4016,"don't call off the wedding!"],[4016,4191,"Please!"],[4191,4358,"Please, for the baby's sake."],[4358,4508,"Please forgive me!"],[4587,4738,"Mother, please!"],[4738,4813,"Please don't do this..."],[4813,4934,"do this for the baby."],[4934,5046,"Please!"],[5046,5159,"Please forgive me."],[5159,5296,"Please!"],[5296,5367,"I'm going to need"],[5367,5476,"more than your word"],[5476,5568,"and a piece of paper."],[5672,5851,"I need a doctor's confirmation,"],[5851,6043,"DNA test included."],[6043,6147,"That is the only proof"],[6147,6302,"that I will accept."],[6302,6439,"Family doctor will run a test."],[6585,6785,"If this is true,"],[6823,6873,"I’ll accept full"],[6873,7073,"responsibility."],[7119,7315,"For the baby,"],[7315,7369,"and for you."]],"30":[[208,229,"Doctor,"],[229,375,"what are the results?"],[654,855,"Mia is pregnant."],[921,1121,"See, Noah?"],[1142,1343,"I wasn’t lying."],[1443,1618,"We will still need a DNA test"],[1618,1659,"to prove that"],[1659,1860,"the baby is Noah's."],[1889,2002,"You still don't trust me,"],[2002,2114,"do you?"],[2114,2314,"Why do you keep denying me?"],[2339,2498,"If the baby is Noah's?"],[2498,2560,"Why are you"],[2560,2761,"scared of taking a test?"],[2765,2915,"Unless you have something"],[2915,3115,"that you're not telling us."],[3219,3415,"I'm not scared."],[3415,3461,"Doctor,"],[3461,3636,"when can we run the test?"],[3636,3807,"The baby's still early-term."],[3807,3945,"I recommend waiting a month"],[3945,4012,"for the most"],[4012,4212,"reliable results."],[4383,4458,"Fine."],[4504,4579,"We’ll wait."],[4696,4796,"If the baby's mine,"],[4796,4863,"then I'll take"],[4863,4934,"full responsibility"],[4934,5134,"for you and the child."],[5163,5251,"But this doesn't cover up"],[5251,5451,"what you did."],[5484,5655,"You’ll still pay for it."],[5655,5764,"I dodged the bullet"],[5764,5826,"this time."],[5826,6026,"But what about next month?"],[6031,6160,"I need to find a way"],[6160,6268,"to protect myself"],[6268,6406,"and this baby."],[6406,6606,"No matter what it takes."]],"31":[[400,546,"Vivian."],[546,720,"I brought you some tea."],[720,800,"No, thank you."],[800,950,"Not much of a tea drinker."],[1046,1180,"How about we go"],[1180,1296,"shopping for baby"],[1296,1423,"clothes together?"],[1423,1633,"I thought it'd be a nice way"],[1633,1770,"for us to bond."],[1770,1926,"Have Anna go with you."],[1926,2126,"I have work to do."],[2140,2240,"Well..."],[2240,2423,"Let me make one thing clear."],[2423,2480,"Your engagement"],[2480,2576,"is over."],[2576,2740,"I'm not your mother-in-law."],[2740,2833,"And you will be gone"],[2833,2943,"in a month."],[2943,3103,"What about Noah's baby?"],[3103,3170,"Does this child"],[3170,3283,"not mean anything to you?"],[3283,3453,"I mean, you're a mother, too."],[3453,3530,"We'll talk about this"],[3530,3590,"next month,"],[3590,3720,"after the test."],[3836,4036,"Ma'am."],[4116,4163,"Catherine's"],[4163,4363,"calling."],[4553,4686,"Catherine?"],[4760,4836,"She's Mr. Harper's"],[4836,4936,"grandmother."],[4936,5076,"She lives in Florida."],[5076,5110,"Her 80th birthday"],[5110,5256,"is coming up, and"],[5256,5323,"Mrs. Harper's"],[5323,5523,"planning a big celebration."],[5660,5776,"Noah always talked"],[5776,5863,"about how much he loves"],[5863,5980,"his grandma."],[5980,6103,"This could be it."],[6103,6163,"If I can get"],[6163,6236,"Noah's grandmother"],[6236,6376,"on my side at the party,"],[6376,6520,"I might still secure my"],[6520,6653,"place in the Harper family."]],"32":[[246,408,"Vivian's impossible."],[408,558,"She does not respond"],[558,675,"to kindness."],[675,796,"And trying to win her over"],[796,992,"is a waste of time."],[1017,1105,"We really did"],[1105,1297,"mess up that day."],[1297,1405,"If we had known who she was,"],[1405,1468,"maybe things would"],[1468,1601,"have been different."],[1601,1714,"Well, I heard that"],[1714,1772,"the real power of"],[1772,1864,"the Harper family"],[1881,1981,"isn’t Vivian."],[2060,2164,"It’s Noah’s grandmother,"],[2164,2302,"Catherine."],[2302,2406,"She's the one in charge."],[2406,2556,"But she stays in Florida"],[2556,2752,"and lets Vivian manage things."],[2752,2798,"Honestly,"],[2840,3011,"you don't need to take her seriously."],[3011,3082,"Exactly."],[3082,3182,"She's just a middle-aged"],[3182,3382,"woman trying to act tough."],[3411,3478,"There's no way"],[3478,3699,"she's running a whole empire."],[3791,3891,"Your only leverage"],[3891,3970,"is this baby."],[3970,4074,"And if anything"],[4074,4295,"happens to it, we're screwed."],[4346,4491,"Did you hear about Jonathan?"],[4491,4658,"He's done."],[4658,4713,"He can't even show"],[4713,4913,"his face in L.A."],[4929,4996,"I guess Mia"],[4996,5080,"hasn't told them who the"],[5080,5280,"baby's father really is."],[5309,5338,"So, Mia,"],[5401,5492,"what’s the plan?"],[5547,5684,"Don't worry about it."],[5684,5743,"I've got everything"],[5743,5943,"under control."],[6047,6101,"So,"],[6189,6302,"what should I get"],[6352,6464,"Noah’s grandmother?"]],"33":[[204,337,"Catherine,"],[337,400,"how have you been feeling"],[400,496,"lately?"],[496,692,"Oh, I've been in the sun"],[692,750,"so much,"],[750,967,"I'm practically glowing."],[1063,1284,"How is the wedding ceremony"],[1284,1484,"coming along for Noah?"],[1530,1793,"Well, the engagement,"],[1793,1906,"it's been delayed."],[1906,2060,"Delayed?"],[2060,2260,"Why? Is Noah ok?"],[2260,2327,"You know."],[2327,2460,"Vivian, you know,"],[2460,2669,"I'm not getting any younger."],[2706,2944,"I'm turning 80 next week,"],[2944,3182,"and I just want to be"],[3182,3315,"a grandma"],[3315,3553,"before it's too late."],[3603,3691,"You know,"],[3691,3816,"the Harper family"],[3816,4137,"just seems so distant"],[4137,4320,"lately."],[4320,4512,"I just want to feel like"],[4512,4713,"a real family again."],[4825,4938,"No, the Harper family"],[4938,5092,"is fine."],[5105,5305,"Nothing bad has happened."],[5839,5893,"Vivian's nothing"],[5893,6093,"but a puppet."],[6106,6147,"It looks like"],[6147,6231,"Noah's grandmother"],[6231,6360,"is the one calling the shots."],[6360,6489,"Her birthday’s next week."],[6489,6681,"This is my last chance."],[6681,6769,"If I can get on her"],[6769,6844,"good side,"],[6844,6973,"I'll secure my spot"],[6973,7094,"in the Harper family."],[7411,7457,"Are the gifts"],[7457,7549,"ready for Catherine?"],[7549,7657,"Yes, ma'am."],[7657,7741,"Mr. George"],[7741,7836,"double-checked everything."],[7836,7924,"It's all set."],[7924,8020,"Thank you, Anna."]],"34":[[291,325,"Why did we"],[325,442,"take the long way, ma'am?"],[442,517,"The media is already"],[517,592,"running wild"],[592,638,"with stories"],[638,686,"about Noah"],[686,809,"and some mysterious lady."],[809,900,"I do not need"],[900,1013,"to stir up things even more."],[1013,1092,"You've always kept"],[1092,1167,"a low profile,"],[1167,1205,"but who'd have thought"],[1205,1372,"it'd cause this much trouble?"],[1372,1493,"You just got back to the U.S.,"],[1493,1593,"so no one in L.A."],[1593,1699,"knows that you're the one"],[1699,1735,"actually running"],[1735,1876,"the business association."],[1876,1993,"And if they did—"],[1993,2106,"That’s enough, Anna."],[2106,2152,"That’s enough."],[2152,2227,"Let’s just get inside."],[2227,2427,"Come on."],[2548,2748,"Invitation, please."],[2765,2890,"I don't have one."],[2890,3061,"I'm so sorry, ma'am."],[3061,3148,"I forgot to"],[3148,3286,"set one aside for you."],[3286,3482,"No invitation, no entry."],[3507,3586,"Who do you think you are"],[3586,3787,"showing up here without one?"],[3841,3970,"Excuse me."],[3970,4054,"Do you even know"],[4054,4179,"who you're talking to?"],[4179,4329,"I don't care who you are."],[4329,4429,"This is a private event"],[4429,4583,"for the Harper family."],[4583,4650,"Who could possibly"],[4650,4725,"outrank this?"],[4725,4825,"Seriously,"],[4825,4950,"who shows up to an event"],[4950,5100,"like this without a car?"],[5242,5263,"What are you?"],[5263,5459,"Lost or something?"],[5459,5522,"Step aside"],[5522,5722,"and let the guests through."],[5772,5972,"I—"],[6101,6285,"Watch your mouth!"],[6289,6460,"This is Mrs. Harper,"],[6460,6619,"Mr. Harper's mother."],[6619,6669,"Mrs. Harper?"],[6669,6765,"Yeah right."],[6765,6848,"And I’m the CEO"],[6848,6952,"of Harper Group."],[7115,7278,"Get Edward now,"],[7278,7386,"our family butler"],[7386,7524,"and event manager."],[7524,7628,"Tell him I need to see him."],[7628,7749,"Please."],[7749,7862,"She knows Edward?"]],"35":[[120,237,"Wow,"],[237,300,"you've really"],[300,354,"done your research."],[354,475,"I can't believe you even know"],[475,588,"who Mr. Edward is."],[588,754,"Enough!"],[754,880,"Get Edward now."],[880,930,"Like Edward"],[930,992,"would ever waste his time"],[992,1163,"on someone like you?"],[1163,1217,"Get out of here"],[1217,1418,"before this gets embarrassing."],[1559,1805,"Welcome Mrs. Harper."],[1805,1910,"Here is our invitation."],[1910,2035,"Want to double-check it?"],[2035,2143,"Of course not."],[2143,2181,"Mr. Edward"],[2181,2289,"already told us"],[2289,2381,"you are coming."],[2381,2439,"Especially with"],[2439,2640,"the baby on the way."],[2765,2944,"Ms. Mia,"],[2944,3103,"you're Mr. Harper's fiancé?"],[3103,3165,"Why don't you"],[3165,3365,"tell them who we are?"],[3407,3603,"Oh, I'm too worn out"],[3603,3787,"for all this commotion."],[3787,3924,"Oh, don't worry Mrs. Harper."],[3924,4124,"We'll take care of them."],[4704,4800,"Get out now"],[4800,5067,"before I throw you out myself."],[5309,5380,"Who exactly were you planning"],[5380,5480,"on throwing out?"]],"36":[[296,462,"What's going on?"],[462,508,"This woman"],[508,600,"claimed to be your mother"],[600,784,"and disrespected Mrs. Stone."],[784,846,"And teaching her"],[846,1005,"a lesson was the right move?"],[1005,1117,"Edward!"],[1117,1147,"So this is"],[1147,1330,"how you're training them now?"],[1330,1526,"You idiot!"],[1555,1609,"Oh!"],[1609,1714,"Do you have any idea"],[1714,1843,"who this is?"],[1843,1968,"Have you lost your mind?"],[2097,2214,"This is Mrs. Harper,"],[2227,2460,"Mr. Harper's mother."],[2748,2969,"My deepest apologies, sir,"],[3019,3090,"madam."],[3174,3219,"I should have"],[3219,3299,"done a better job"],[3299,3424,"at keeping my subordinates"],[3424,3482,"in line."],[3549,3670,"They not only embarrassed me,"],[3670,3774,"they also humiliated"],[3774,3866,"my mother."],[3891,4041,"You're absolutely right, sir."],[4041,4124,"And whatever punishment"],[4124,4212,"you see fit,"],[4212,4412,"I will humbly accept."],[4496,4617,"You moron!"],[4742,4904,"Apologize to Mr. Harper"],[4904,5009,"and his mother"],[5009,5209,"right now!"],[5263,5376,"We apologize!"],[5376,5518,"We didn't know who you were."],[5518,5655,"Please forgive us."],[5655,5722,"Enough!"],[5722,5922,"Get up."],[6197,6235,"Edward,"],[6235,6406,"if this happens again,"],[6406,6452,"you're done"],[6452,6544,"as head steward."],[6544,6660,"Understood, sir!"],[6710,6802,"Please."]],"37":[[788,909,"Okay, well."],[942,1026,"Mom,"],[1026,1084,"everything's set up"],[1084,1284,"exactly how grandma likes it."],[1305,1326,"Oh."],[1326,1426,"So thoughtful."],[1426,1534,"So nice."],[1572,1768,"Is that Noah’s secret mistress?"],[1793,1993,"And he brought her here?"],[1993,2035,"Man,"],[2035,2127,"only rich people pull"],[2127,2239,"stunts like this."],[2239,2381,"Watch what you're saying."],[2381,2427,"This is"],[2427,2590,"Mrs. Catherine Harper's birthday."],[2606,2761,"Show some respect."],[2861,3015,"That's her daughter-in-law."],[3015,3211,"She's got back from overseas."],[3253,3378,"I gotta go pick up grandma now."],[3378,3499,"But let me know if"],[3499,3611,"anything else happens."],[3611,3670,"Of course."],[3670,3870,"I will be fine."],[4220,4283,"Showing up"],[4283,4412,"to a huge birthday party"],[4412,4612,"like this empty-handed."],[4625,4800,"That's pretty bold."],[4800,4842,"Mia, I'm sure"],[4842,4925,"the gift you got"],[4925,5030,"for Mr. Harper's grandmother"],[5030,5201,"will blow her away."],[5217,5351,"She'll be so proud of her"],[5351,5388,"thoughtful"],[5388,5547,"granddaughter in law."],[5547,5672,"Nothing makes a grandmother"],[5672,5872,"happier than a new baby."],[5893,6076,"Once the little one comes,"],[6076,6335,"it'll be the best gift of all."],[6335,6527,"Exactly what this family needs."],[6652,6831,"Oh, let's toast,"],[6831,6923,"Vivian."],[7394,7557,"It's a very special day"],[7557,7657,"today."],[8124,8191,"Ahhh!"],[8579,8700,"Why did you push me?"],[8700,8817,"How could you push her,"],[8817,8921,"Mrs. Harper?"],[8921,9000,"She's carrying the"],[9000,9163,"Harper family bloodline."]],"38":[[229,316,"A mother-in-law"],[316,442,"pushing her"],[442,546,"pregnant daughter-in-law."],[546,688,"That is brutal."],[688,871,"Way over the line."],[871,1009,"Wow."],[1009,1159,"I guess Mia was right."],[1159,1330,"You never liked her."],[1330,1426,"She proved it"],[1426,1605,"to everyone here."],[1605,1701,"Mia,"],[1701,1801,"your performances"],[1801,1993,"are getting better and better."],[1993,2189,"Too bad I didn't touch you."],[2198,2335,"I wasn't trying"],[2335,2448,"to cause any trouble."],[2448,2506,"I just"],[2560,2740,"wanted us to be closer."],[2740,2836,"I know you don't want—"],[2836,2973,"Closer?"],[2994,3132,"Are you kidding me?"],[3132,3294,"You refuse to believe"],[3294,3400,"this baby is Noah's"],[3400,3495,"and now this?"],[3553,3749,"I know you don't like me,"],[3753,3962,"but why deny your own"],[4024,4225,"grandchild?"],[4262,4304,"Whether this is"],[4304,4425,"Noah's baby,"],[4425,4546,"or isn't,"],[4546,4729,"it's not up to you."],[4729,4808,"The DNA test"],[4808,4938,"will tell the truth."],[5005,5196,"You're just jealous."],[5196,5256,"You have this"],[5256,5356,"strange relationship"],[5356,5526,"with your son."],[5559,5693,"You can't stand that I'm"],[5693,5784,"the most important woman"],[5784,5972,"in his life now."],[5972,6168,"You just wanted control over Noah."],[6197,6339,"For someone like you,"],[6343,6539,"Mrs. Harper, is pitiful."],[6639,6773,"The security footage"],[6773,6973,"will tell the truth."],[6990,7052,"Mia,"],[7140,7240,"if I wanted"],[7240,7328,"to hurt your baby,"],[7328,7503,"why would I wait until now?"],[7520,7716,"Stop lying already, Mia."]],"39":[[0,66,"I just,"],[66,266,"I just wanted a happy family."],[325,467,"I don't know why you hate me"],[467,667,"so much."],[800,975,"Everyone saw it."],[975,1151,"You pushed me."],[1151,1276,"That's right."],[1276,1451,"We all saw it."],[1451,1651,"She shut me up."],[1701,1830,"If this hurts Mia"],[1830,1943,"or the baby,"],[1943,2122,"who will take responsibility?"],[2122,2314,"Two lives are at stake."],[2414,2515,"Mia."],[2535,2602,"I never thought"],[2602,2740,"you would stoop this low."],[2740,2844,"Hurting yourself"],[2844,3044,"to play the victim?"],[3103,3299,"But listen carefully."],[3299,3499,"No matter how low you go,"],[3507,3574,"no matter what"],[3574,3753,"stunt you pull,"],[3753,3916,"you will never"],[3916,4116,"be a part of this family."],[4149,4350,"This is"],[4350,4567,"who the real Vivian Harper is."],[4721,4850,"She hides behind her power"],[4850,5013,"and money,"],[5013,5209,"but she's heartless!"],[5209,5317,"She's pregnant."],[5317,5376,"Shouldn't we get her"],[5376,5547,"to a hospital or something?"],[5547,5714,"This party is over."],[5714,5755,"It was over"],[5755,5847,"before it started."],[5847,5893,"These two"],[5893,5968,"are going to"],[5968,6131,"tear the family apart."],[6131,6243,"You don't deserve to be"],[6243,6398,"her mother in law."],[6398,6535,"Everyone."],[6535,6673,"We should kick her out."],[6673,6727,"Yeah, yeah."],[6727,6869,"Kick her out already!"],[6869,6990,"Exactly."],[6990,7127,"And if anything happens"],[7127,7219,"to Mia's baby,"],[7219,7457,"Vivian Harper is the murderer!"],[7536,7611,"Are we just"],[7611,7703,"gonna let her get away"],[7703,7791,"with this?"],[7791,7916,"Oh no, kick her out of here already."],[7916,8020,"Yeah. Get out!"],[8020,8266,"I'd like to see anyone try."]],"40":[[45,141,"Catherine."],[141,221,"Ma'am!"],[475,525,"Ma'am,"],[525,646,"Vivian pushed me."],[1155,1272,"Thank you all"],[1272,1459,"for coming to celebrate"],[1472,1726,"an old lady's birthday."],[1851,2039,"All the noise."],[2064,2131,"Vivian,"],[2131,2243,"you planned"],[2243,2406,"a lovely party,"],[2456,2690,"but the theatrics are"],[2706,2886,"unnecessary."],[3048,3244,"Let me be clear."],[3324,3556,"If anyone wants to"],[3556,3778,"stir up any trouble tonight,"],[3883,4166,"you will answer to me."],[4279,4375,"I'm,"],[4375,4567,"I'm Noah's fiancee."],[4683,4863,"I don't mean to make a scene"],[4863,4934,"or anything."],[4934,5009,"It's just that"],[5096,5159,"Vivian"],[5230,5438,"accidentally pushed me earlier."],[5497,5789,"I know Vivian very well."],[5860,6131,"And if you didn't provoke her."],[6172,6443,"She's not the type of person"],[6531,6894,"who acts without reason."],[6948,7065,"I never touched her."],[7102,7165,"You can check"],[7165,7286,"the security footage"],[7286,7374,"for proof."],[7407,7436,"Mom"],[7436,7478,"you don't need to"],[7478,7582,"defend yourself."],[7582,7649,"It's something"],[7649,7720,"that she wouldn't do."],[7766,7820,"Mia."],[8133,8212,"What are you up to?"],[8420,8608,"Ma'am, I'm so sorry."],[8608,8800,"I must have been overwhelmed."],[8929,9109,"Nervous about the baby."],[9109,9188,"I panicked"],[9188,9380,"and lost my balance."],[9388,9434,"I,"],[9513,9655,"maybe I overreacted"],[9655,9722,"a little bit,"],[9759,9889,"but I was just nervous."],[9889,9964,"I was so worried"],[9964,10068,"about the baby."],[10151,10260,"You are pregnant?"]],"41":[[87,145,"Yes,"],[262,337,"I'm carrying"],[337,442,"Noah's baby."],[754,934,"This is great news"],[934,1063,"for our family."],[1096,1146,"Why didn't you"],[1146,1209,"tell me"],[1209,1368,"on the phone earlier?"],[1384,1534,"We had to wait a week"],[1534,1605,"back then."],[1614,1693,"But we just got"],[1693,1847,"the DNA test today"],[1847,1926,"to confirm."],[1981,2127,"DNA results?"],[2193,2385,"From the moment I saved him"],[2385,2510,"from that accident."],[2510,2823,"I've given everything"],[2873,2952,"for Noah."],[3119,3274,"I wasn't able to recognize Vivian,"],[3315,3482,"and I disrespected her."],[3482,3616,"And I am sorry."],[3862,4091,"If Noah and Vivian"],[4091,4225,"can't forgive me,"],[4258,4366,"I'll leave."],[4554,4725,"If it makes things easier,"],[4725,4767,"I’ll,"],[4950,5171,"I’ll end this pregnancy!"],[5238,5426,"Oh, sweetheart,"],[5480,5672,"don't even think about that."],[5843,6085,"Why are you considering"],[6085,6235,"DNA testing?"],[6289,6431,"That could be dangerous"],[6431,6539,"for the baby."],[6539,6710,"This is absurd."],[6731,6802,"Grandma, it's not"],[6802,6877,"what you think."],[6877,6927,"It's—"],[7002,7061,"She's—"],[7061,7136,"Mia,"],[7173,7319,"you're expected."],[7374,7632,"And your health is priority."],[7716,7903,"And if anything happens,"],[7912,8062,"you come to me"],[8116,8199,"directly."],[8400,8466,"Vivian,"],[8554,8742,"you are her mother-in-law."],[8804,9034,"Show some compassion."],[9146,9288,"You should know better"],[9288,9534,"than anyone as a Harper."],[9592,9843,"It's family first."],[9901,10005,"Yes, I do."],[10026,10080,"Oh please"],[10080,10193,"don't be upset with her."],[10285,10372,"I promise,"],[10372,10518,"no matter what happens."],[10573,10714,"I'll take care of this baby."],[10756,10935,"You are so thoughtful."],[11119,11232,"For your birthday,"],[11307,11465,"I prepared something"],[11465,11586,"very special."],[11803,11886,"Bring in the gifts."]],"42":[[95,271,"I hear you're a fan"],[271,387,"of rare collectibles,"],[387,654,"so I found this royal tiara"],[654,779,"worn by the former"],[779,867,"Queen of England"],[867,1001,"just for you."],[1001,1109,"It's priceless,"],[1109,1393,"and it's over a century old."],[1451,1697,"This tiara is a symbol"],[1697,1851,"of your timeless elegance"],[1851,1922,"and grace."],[1964,2139,"A true tiara,"],[2168,2256,"priceless,"],[2256,2335,"timeless,"],[2335,2502,"and utterly exquisite."],[2502,2656,"She's put real thought"],[2656,2727,"into this gift."],[2756,2919,"What an impressive gift."],[2986,3082,"Oh, Mia."],[3082,3274,"You’ve outdone yourself."],[3382,3591,"Hearing of your love of art."],[3687,3812,"I tracked down"],[3891,4062,"this wonderful treasure."],[4141,4270,"Whispers of the Morning Light"],[4270,4421,"by Amelia Winter."],[4471,4596,"It's crafted"],[4596,4742,"with rare pigments"],[4742,4875,"and precision techniques,"],[4875,5030,"making it at least"],[5030,5276,"$10 million."],[5313,5451,"Amelia winter?"],[5488,5638,"Her works are legendary."],[5655,5739,"Honestly,"],[5739,5839,"that could be worth"],[5839,5989,"way more than 10 million."],[6093,6164,"Oh,"],[6247,6544,"I love anyone who appreciates"],[6564,6706,"fine art."],[6769,7007,"Mia, you certainly do know"],[7007,7165,"how to butter people up."],[7207,7298,"What do you mean?"],[7344,7457,"I've worked hard"],[7486,7653,"to find meaningful gifts"],[7699,7820,"for Mrs. Catherine."],[7870,7957,"Are you saying you can do"],[7957,8020,"better?"],[8078,8174,"In due time,"],[8174,8233,"you will see"],[8233,8333,"the difference between us."]],"43":[[12,100,"In due time,"],[100,162,"you will see"],[162,296,"the difference between us."],[308,392,"Difference?"],[467,658,"I'm not finished yet."],[742,867,"Ma’am,"],[955,1230,"my third gift to you..."],[1468,1643,"A beach front mansion"],[1643,1768,"in Malibu."],[2064,2227,"In the exclusive"],[2227,2414,"Crimson Beach area."],[2464,2677,"Oh, goodness."],[2727,2844,"Malibu?"],[2844,2948,"That's prime real estate,"],[2948,3107,"but crimson beach?"],[3140,3249,"Oh my god."],[3269,3457,"It's a gesture of goodwill"],[3457,3599,"from my family"],[3599,3720,"to the Harpers."],[3803,3874,"All I ask"],[3874,4074,"is just your blessing for"],[4141,4341,"me and my child to stay"],[4341,4642,"and for my marriage to Noah."],[4692,4792,"Grandma,"],[4792,4838,"these gifts"],[4838,4929,"don't mean anything."],[4950,5046,"I will take responsibility"],[5046,5096,"for the baby."],[5096,5188,"But I'm not going to"],[5188,5246,"marry"],[5280,5334,"Mia."],[5634,5718,"Really."],[5772,5864,"It looks like the stones"],[5864,5989,"hardly try."],[5989,6043,"They just threw in"],[6043,6214,"some random mansion"],[6214,6373,"to appease Catherine."],[6389,6439,"Ma'am,"],[6439,6535,"the mansion is worth"],[6535,6673,"50 million."],[6673,6777,"We had to pull a lot"],[6777,6894,"of strings to get that."],[6973,7048,"And who are you"],[7048,7186,"to question us?"],[7228,7386,"I bet you couldn't"],[7386,7453,"even manage to"],[7453,7536,"get a property"],[7536,7670,"on Crimson Beach."],[7720,7791,"That mansion is"],[7791,7816,"one of the"],[7816,8008,"most exclusive in LA,"],[8024,8145,"and she has the nerve"],[8145,8249,"to call it trash?"],[8345,8408,"Are you sure"],[8408,8487,"that mansion is"],[8487,8525,"in the middle"],[8525,8637,"of Crimson Beach?"],[8696,8888,"How does she know it isn't?"],[8929,9046,"Because I've owned"],[9046,9167,"Wavesong Villa,"],[9209,9355,"the most expensive"],[9355,9551,"beachfront property in L.A."],[9626,9684,"for a while now."]],"44":[[29,250,"Vivian, when did you get"],[291,462,"Wavesong Villa?"],[462,592,"Mia, admit it."],[592,658,"That house is not"],[658,804,"in the center of Crimson Beach."],[804,896,"Fine."],[955,1130,"It's not in the center."],[1130,1213,"But it's only because"],[1213,1317,"when I tried"],[1317,1405,"to buy that place,"],[1488,1547,"Wavesong Villa"],[1547,1647,"was already taken."],[1647,1872,"So I had to settle for Sunset Villa"],[1872,2010,"over in the northeast."],[2135,2298,"Wait, so Ms. Stone's mansion"],[2298,2456,"isn't even prime real estate?"],[2481,2531,"Wow,"],[2531,2585,"Vivian bought"],[2585,2686,"Wavesong Villa?"],[2698,2827,"What a bold move."],[2973,3044,"So Mia,"],[3098,3211,"now that Catherine is around,"],[3211,3311,"are you done sucking up?"],[3349,3415,"I have someone"],[3415,3531,"monitoring all the money"],[3531,3616,"that flows in and out"],[3616,3695,"of the Harper Corp."],[3732,3883,"If she bought Wavesong Villa,"],[3883,4020,"I'd be the first to know."],[4091,4204,"This doesn't prove"],[4204,4279,"that Wavesong Villa"],[4279,4396,"is yours."],[4408,4466,"Mia's right."],[4483,4546,"Wavesong is worth"],[4546,4625,"more than twice"],[4625,4742,"as much as Sunset Villa."],[4846,4888,"If anyone"],[4888,4963,"snatched it up,"],[5005,5088,"everyone would know."],[5188,5321,"Mom, did you really buy"],[5321,5392,"Wavesong Villa?"],[5401,5593,"That's quite the purchase..."],[5613,5743,"I have someone on their way"],[5743,5793,"right now"],[5793,5839,"with the deed"],[5839,5930,"to the property."],[6193,6322,"Vivian you're bluffing,"],[6423,6564,"just to make me look bad."],[6598,6644,"There's"],[6644,6848,"no way you could ever afford"],[6848,6936,"a place like that"],[6936,7032,"on your own."],[7048,7144,"Let’s see if you think"],[7144,7215,"I'm still bluffing"],[7215,7298,"in five minutes."]],"45":[[33,179,"Oh Vivian."],[212,342,"Mia’s gifts are"],[342,542,"genuine and heartfelt."],[588,788,"And nothing you can say"],[788,925,"can change that."],[963,1188,"I just wanted to make"],[1222,1413,"Grandma Catharine happy,"],[1422,1655,"so that us harpers"],[1655,1906,"could be a big, happy family."],[2052,2239,"But I guess"],[2323,2515,"you're never satisfied."],[2527,2573,"Mia—"],[2573,2823,"Stop causing trouble."],[2923,3023,"If people knew"],[3023,3174,"you were competing"],[3207,3357,"with your daughter-in-law,"],[3357,3611,"you'd be the joke of the city!"],[3636,3724,"I'm not trying to compete"],[3724,3787,"with Mia."],[3816,3928,"It's just that"],[3928,4058,"her cheap gifts"],[4058,4154,"are an insult"],[4154,4270,"to the Harper family."],[4320,4441,"Are you calling"],[4441,4775,"my carefully chosen gifts cheap?"],[4821,4917,"Am I wrong?"],[5030,5142,"These gifts are nice."],[5301,5509,"Maybe not more than 20 million?"],[5622,5722,"Extravagant"],[5722,5830,"maybe even to the"],[5855,5968,"untrained eye."],[6026,6189,"But you have to do a lot more"],[6189,6310,"than that to impress me."]],"46":[[33,162,"What the hell,"],[162,254,"Vivian!"],[271,304,"Mom,"],[304,396,"maybe calm down."],[442,513,"Vivian,"],[608,834,"you've ruined the Stone Family gifts!"],[880,1067,"You are seriously evil."],[1113,1159,"Jeez,"],[1159,1301,"Catherine looks furious."],[1338,1480,"Vivian's in trouble now."],[1564,1735,"They're all ruined!"],[1764,1839,"God."],[1981,2027,"Ma'am,"],[2027,2168,"you have to get back at her."],[2281,2360,"The Harpers want"],[2360,2489,"nothing from you."],[2569,2598,"Ma’am,"],[2602,2702,"she keeps trashing"],[2702,2781,"on my birthday gifts"],[2781,2848,"when she can't even"],[2848,2932,"do better herself."],[2932,3048,"I mean, come on!"],[3098,3294,"She showed up empty-handed."],[3424,3582,"George should be here by now."],[3653,3908,"I can so do better than her."],[3916,4041,"I can easily"],[4108,4229,"do better than her."],[4266,4371,"Everybody knows that"],[4371,4479,"Vivian is masquerading"],[4479,4562,"as this fake"],[4562,4617,"strong"],[4617,4717,"independent woman,"],[4717,4783,"living off her"],[4783,4892,"family's money."],[4934,5080,"If she wasn't a Harper,"],[5080,5259,"she'd be a broke nobody."],[5309,5417,"Mia's got a point."],[5417,5476,"Harper's wealth is"],[5476,5609,"thanks to Catherine and Noah,"],[5622,5718,"not Vivian."],[5739,5864,"Vivian talks the game."],[5864,5955,"Can she actually"],[5955,6035,"back it up?"],[6481,6560,"Stop!"],[6560,6669,"What are you doing?"],[6756,6815,"No!"],[6815,6927,"That’s the deed!"],[8062,8158,"The tiara,"],[8158,8312,"the mansion, the painting."],[8312,8383,"I'll pay you back"],[8383,8462,"double for everything."],[8575,8696,"Ma'am, she's out of control."],[8696,8821,"Please do something."]],"47":[[116,271,"Isn't that George Jones,"],[271,387,"president of"],[387,521,"the L.A. Chamber of Commerce?"],[521,617,"The man who controls"],[617,742,"the internal operations"],[742,834,"of Harbor Corp"],[834,1005,"and every major business"],[1005,1101,"in the city?"],[1101,1159,"You know,"],[1159,1234,"I heard that"],[1234,1351,"he's just a figurehead."],[1351,1630,"But how does he know Mrs. Harper?"],[1639,1793,"Who the hell is Vivian Harper"],[1793,1864,"anyway?"],[1931,2118,"I present a Cartier brooch"],[2135,2344,"once belonging to a former first lady"],[2344,2481,"of the United States."],[2506,2581,"Wait,"],[2619,2790,"wasn't that sold at auction recently"],[2790,3040,"for 100 million?"],[3144,3257,"How did it get here?"],[3703,3787,"The title"],[3816,4041,"to a 200 foot superyacht."],[4108,4191,"Superyacht?"],[4191,4366,"That's the pinnacle of luxury."],[4471,4562,"A portrait"],[4583,4721,"of Mrs. Katherine Harper,"],[4742,4925,"painted by the one and only"],[4925,5034,"Amelia Winter."],[5351,5447,"Wait."],[5447,5534,"Amelia Winter"],[5534,5726,"retired ages ago."],[5743,5784,"I can't believe"],[5784,5843,"she would come"],[5843,5935,"out of retirement"],[5935,6043,"to paint a portrait"],[6043,6110,"for someone."],[6110,6268,"If Vivan really persuaded her"],[6268,6381,"to come out of retirement,"],[6381,6477,"this portrait is worth"],[6477,6631,"way more than the painting"],[6631,6715,"that Mia brought."],[6760,7002,"The Deed to Wavesong Villa"],[7032,7173,"located in the heart"],[7173,7273,"of Crimson Beach."],[7453,7607,"So Mrs. Harper really did"],[7607,7711,"get Wavesong."],[7766,7795,"You know,"],[7795,7891,"I've heard rumors"],[7891,7953,"of her clout,"],[7953,8224,"but this is on a whole other level."],[8308,8433,"And security will bring along"],[8433,8512,"royal jewelry,"],[8512,8646,"watches and handbags"],[8646,8796,"from the 18th century."],[8875,9063,"All absolute masterpieces."],[9109,9196,"Vivian could have started"],[9196,9255,"a museum"],[9255,9300,"with all those"],[9300,9376,"rare artifacts,"],[9376,9476,"but gave them"],[9476,9576,"as gifts instead."]],"48":[[4,116,"These aren't just gifts."],[116,191,"She gave the lady"],[191,379,"a goddamn treasure chest."],[487,571,"This can't be all"],[571,688,"from one person."],[809,984,"It’s unthinkable."],[1046,1138,"Mrs. Harper's a widow."],[1138,1184,"Where would she get"],[1184,1305,"all the money for this?"],[1305,1372,"There's a rumor"],[1372,1488,"that she's the CEO"],[1488,1572,"of Harper Corp"],[1572,1735,"and the richest woman in LA."],[1735,1818,"Must be true."],[1868,2060,"Her wealth is unmatched."],[2114,2181,"God,"],[2181,2339,"I way underestimated her."],[2435,2485,"I mean,"],[2502,2631,"I took on some crazy debt"],[2631,2798,"to afford all those gifts."],[2819,2927,"Trying to one-up her"],[2927,3044,"was the wrong move."],[3073,3299,"Mr. Jones."],[3332,3486,"It's so nice to see you"],[3486,3561,"in person."],[3561,3762,"Had I known you'd be here,"],[3762,3878,"I would've rolled out"],[3878,4045,"the red carpet."],[4091,4141,"Please"],[4141,4425,"excuse our lack of preparedness."],[4504,4546,"Ma’am,"],[4546,4642,"you flatter me."],[4688,4758,"Vivian,"],[4758,4892,"where on earth"],[4892,5071,"did you get the funds?"],[5146,5292,"I mean, this is practically"],[5292,5609,"worth half the Harper fortune."],[5655,5730,"Mrs. Harper."],[5818,5851,"I brought"],[5851,5951,"everything you asked for."],[6001,6064,"I hope you find it"],[6064,6147,"to be sufficient."]],"49":[[4,91,"Vivian,"],[112,304,"what's this all about?"],[358,437,"I'm sorry"],[437,525,"that I didn't tell you"],[525,592,"sooner."],[658,767,"I'm behind"],[767,934,"the L.A. Chamber of Commerce."],[971,1038,"I've used"],[1038,1146,"my extensive connections"],[1146,1300,"and networks abroad"],[1300,1443,"to curate these items"],[1443,1576,"for the last few years."],[1651,1705,"So, mom,"],[1705,1789,"you're the one that's"],[1789,1872,"calling all the shots"],[1872,1956,"behind the scenes?"],[1976,2122,"My God!"],[2122,2202,"The elusive"],[2202,2357,"Chamber of Commerce president"],[2357,2623,"is Mrs. Harper herself."],[2623,2811,"No wonder she's so loaded."],[2869,3061,"Ma'am, Vivian spent years"],[3061,3190,"collecting all these items"],[3190,3261,"for you."],[3261,3453,"Oh, Vivian,"],[3503,3682,"you're the sweetest daughter-in-law"],[3682,3895,"and so generous."],[3945,4191,"No, I don't believe it."],[4295,4387,"She couldn't have done this"],[4387,4471,"all on her own."],[4583,4804,"Where did you get these gifts?"],[4850,4895,"I know"],[4895,5021,"they didn't come from her."],[5125,5317,"Shut your mouth!"],[5372,5484,"How dare you"],[5484,5734,"insult my daughter-in-law!"],[5872,5930,"Mia."],[5980,6126,"I know those gifts"],[6126,6197,"were your way"],[6197,6297,"of securing your place"],[6297,6423,"in the Harper family."],[6439,6523,"It's a nice drawing,"],[6523,6585,"really."],[6610,6698,"It's too bad they're"],[6698,6815,"all terrible fakes."]],"50":[[179,308,"You're lying!"],[308,442,"This is slander!"],[625,784,"If this tiara is real,"],[784,959,"the Royal Family's markings"],[984,1059,"would be inside."],[1151,1288,"These markings are fake."],[1309,1384,"Liar!"],[1405,1555,"I paid a collector"],[1555,1664,"half a million for that."],[1664,1776,"Shall we check?"],[1922,1985,"Come look."],[2043,2181,"What are you doing?"],[2385,2485,"The markings inside of this"],[2485,2590,"are from"],[2590,2698,"a second-rate jeweler."],[2698,2957,"No queen has ever worn this."],[3136,3203,"It's nothing"],[3244,3340,"but a second-"],[3503,3561,"rate,"],[3703,3774,"cheap"],[3991,4037,"copy."]],"51":[[16,120,"That collector"],[120,241,"pulled a fast one on me."],[258,379,"The collector was it?"],[442,496,"What about the"],[496,625,"Whispers of the Morning Light"],[625,671,"painting?"],[688,800,"Same collector, right?"],[850,963,"The painting's fake, too?"],[963,1109,"Holy shit!"],[1109,1180,"I thought it was signed"],[1180,1313,"by the painter herself."],[1484,1551,"Catherine,"],[1593,1718,"Mia is nothing"],[1764,1872,"but a schemer,"],[1885,2002,"with no morals."],[2302,2456,"She cannot marry"],[2456,2519,"Noah."],[2652,2731,"There's no reason"],[2731,2827,"for us to believe"],[2840,2936,"that she's being honest"],[2936,3128,"about carrying Noah’s child."],[3224,3307,"Grandma."],[3424,3511,"I took Mia to get her"],[3511,3591,"DNA test"],[3591,3657,"in the last week."],[3812,3895,"Expecting the results"],[3895,3966,"back today."],[4183,4279,"Like I said before."],[4300,4366,"I’ll take care of the kid"],[4366,4433,"if it's mine."],[4546,4642,"I'm not marrying Mia."],[5017,5042,"Ma'am,"],[5042,5209,"I've devoted years"],[5209,5326,"to the Harper family"],[5326,5430,"and to Noah."],[5568,5663,"I, please..."],[5722,5814,"Please, I..."],[5868,5926,"I want to be"],[5926,6064,"part of this family."],[6064,6197,"Oh, enough."],[6197,6364,"You've been nothing but chaos"],[6364,6648,"to the Harper family."],[6827,6948,"You'll never"],[6990,7082,"be a Harper."]],"52":[[33,70,"If she could"],[70,175,"lie to the head"],[175,271,"of the Harper family."],[271,375,"She'd lie to anyone."],[375,417,"This chick"],[417,567,"is getting what she deserves."],[667,742,"Ma'am."],[838,938,"Think about the baby."],[938,1067,"You wouldn't want the baby"],[1067,1117,"to grow up"],[1117,1234,"without a mother!"],[1434,1589,"After tonight,"],[1626,1818,"you're dead to us."],[3357,3399,"Mia,"],[3399,3507,"snap out of it!"],[3520,3549,"God,"],[3549,3645,"what am I going to do?"],[3661,3828,"I stole this Sunset Villa deed"],[3828,3945,"from my dad."],[4012,4191,"If he finds out it's missing,"],[4191,4262,"I’m finished!"],[4262,4429,"Mia you have to fix this!"],[4429,4546,"I'm already finished."],[4587,4717,"And it's all because of that"],[4771,4904,"Vivian Harper."],[4963,5071,"She's pushed me"],[5071,5163,"this far."],[5284,5472,"So don’t blame me"],[5538,5676,"for what happens next."]],"53":[[375,479,"Vivian."],[517,763,"I opened a new tea business"],[763,850,"recently,"],[955,1113,"and I had"],[1113,1409,"a special peppermint blend"],[1509,1701,"made just for you."],[1851,1989,"Try some."],[2022,2139,"Thank you, Catherine."],[2139,2206,"I know you've been"],[2206,2339,"a tea connoisseur for years,"],[2339,2431,"so I know it will be"],[2431,2548,"top of the line."],[2923,2990,"Madam,"],[3186,3249,"enjoy."],[3261,3332,"Thank you."],[3712,3883,"Fresh tea's get a kick to it,"],[3928,4099,"but this has no smell at all."],[4099,4220,"Something's off."]],"54":[[20,83,"You know,"],[104,171,"I think Mia"],[171,262,"should have some too."],[379,508,"Peppermint tea is known"],[508,654,"to relieve nausea symptoms"],[654,779,"in expectant mothers."],[804,955,"Oh, no."],[955,1101,"I'm good. Thanks."],[1101,1172,"I wouldn't"],[1172,1326,"want to deny you"],[1326,1480,"Catherine’s tea."],[1526,1614,"Nonsense."],[1735,1885,"We can't let word getting out"],[1885,1956,"that the Harpers"],[1956,2064,"are a bad host."],[2118,2310,"You make a good point."],[2364,2456,"Edward."],[3595,3649,"What's wrong,"],[3649,3699,"Mia?"],[3757,3841,"Are you refusing"],[3841,3937,"Catherine's tea?"],[4033,4079,"No,"],[4225,4283,"no."],[4329,4446,"Nothing's wrong."],[5138,5167,"Okay,"],[5167,5221,"what's wrong?"],[5347,5438,"Did you poison it?"],[5438,5501,"Is it poisoned?"]],"55":[[538,625,"What are you"],[625,804,"freaking out about?"],[846,1071,"You were looking so confident"],[1071,1146,"when you brought"],[1146,1267,"the gifts in."],[1372,1451,"Why does it look like"],[1451,1559,"there's something mixed in"],[1559,1655,"with the tea?"],[1701,1768,"The tea has been"],[1768,1876,"tampered with."],[1968,2047,"Ryan,"],[2185,2306,"check the security cameras."],[2356,2431,"Especially the ones"],[2431,2498,"in the kitchen."],[2506,2548,"On it."],[2765,2857,"Speak up."],[2932,3036,"Why did you do it?"],[3774,3870,"Noah’s grandmother"],[3870,3966,"still wants the baby,"],[3966,4054,"but Mrs. Harper is"],[4054,4170,"standing in her way."],[4258,4325,"You know,"],[4387,4500,"I heard"],[4500,4558,"that the old lady"],[4558,4642,"had a special"],[4642,4713,"peppermint tea blend"],[4713,4884,"made especially for Mrs. Harper."],[5505,5584,"This must be it."],[6794,6890,"If I can't stay"],[6890,6977,"in the Harper family,"],[6998,7082,"then Vivian can't"],[7082,7173,"stay on this earth."],[8316,8445,"Come on, tell us."],[8533,8692,"Why did you try to poison me?"],[8842,8896,"I don't know"],[8896,9009,"what you're talking about."]],"56":[[45,325,"This is attempted murder!"],[404,667,"I didn't touch the tea."],[667,763,"It wasn't me!"],[871,938,"Boss,"],[988,1146,"I found traces of cyanide powder"],[1146,1242,"on the kitchen floor."],[1267,1413,"There's surveillance footage too."],[1822,1947,"I didn't do anything."],[2002,2089,"Bella was hungry,"],[2089,2214,"so we went into the kitchen"],[2214,2293,"to get food."],[2335,2485,"Noah, you know me."],[2535,2623,"I wouldn't"],[2623,2677,"even know"],[2677,2819,"how to poison somebody."],[3028,3140,"It couldn't have been me."],[3140,3215,"It's true."],[3253,3340,"I just went with Mia"],[3340,3440,"to get something to eat."],[3474,3695,"Assault and kidnaping."],[3762,3849,"That's going to get you"],[3849,3978,"a couple years in prison."],[4095,4158,"But now you"],[4158,4308,"tried to poison me."],[4358,4383,"You could be"],[4383,4517,"locked away for life."],[4579,4658,"Guards."],[4763,4854,"Take them away."],[5117,5167,"No, no. Let go of me."],[5251,5330,"I don't want to go to jail."],[5351,5409,"Mia,"],[5409,5559,"you can't abandon me."],[5584,5776,"I did this as a favor to you."],[5847,5943,"It was Bella."],[5943,6010,"She did it."],[6010,6093,"I'm innocent."]],"57":[[20,116,"Really Mia?"],[187,342,"You're the mastermind"],[342,425,"behind all of this."],[425,496,"It was you"],[496,646,"who told us to strip Vivian"],[646,709,"and beat her up."],[709,763,"It was you"],[763,817,"who filmed that"],[817,896,"explicit video"],[896,988,"that went viral."],[988,1063,"You only have"],[1063,1167,"the deed to Sunset Vlilla,"],[1167,1284,"because I gave it to you."],[1284,1355,"And you're the one"],[1355,1547,"who told us to poison Mia."],[1551,1605,"I..."],[1659,1758,"That's everything."],[1768,1835,"That's everything."],[1835,1972,"It has nothing to do with me."],[1972,2097,"Please."],[2097,2239,"I don't want to go to jail."],[2239,2327,"Shut up!"],[2573,2681,"If you guys"],[2681,2752,"haven't convinced me"],[2752,2894,"that Noah was cheating on me,"],[2894,2990,"I would never jump"],[2990,3153,"to conclusions about Vivian."],[3190,3390,"And if you hadn't given me"],[3390,3520,"the cyanide powder"],[3520,3611,"and told me about the tea,"],[3611,3724,"I wouldn't have been tricked"],[3724,3853,"into poisoning it."],[3949,4054,"She's been the one"],[4054,4195,"who has been manipulating me"],[4195,4283,"this whole time."],[4491,4600,"Enough!"],[4633,4813,"Take them both away."],[4950,4996,"Wait."],[5038,5217,"Mr. Harper, I know Mia’s secrets."],[5217,5313,"I will tell you all of them"],[5313,5405,"if you spare me."],[5559,5622,"Her secrets?"]],"58":[[12,200,"No, I don't have any secrets."],[208,333,"She's just lying."],[504,558,"Mr. Harper,"],[558,613,"if you agreed"],[613,699,"not to press charges"],[699,763,"against me,"],[763,888,"I will tell you everything"],[888,950,"that I know."],[1167,1309,"Depends what these secrets are."],[1447,1530,"Bella, seriously."],[1530,1601,"Shut up!"],[1601,1630,"Mia,"],[1630,1747,"you sold me out."],[1747,1810,"I am just"],[1810,1910,"returning the favor."],[1997,2147,"Stop yapping!"],[2206,2335,"Or I'll rip"],[2335,2469,"your goddamn tongue out!"],[2519,2606,"Go on."],[2794,2852,"Talk."],[3090,3190,"She's been scamming you"],[3190,3286,"since day one."],[3566,3707,"Remember the car accident?"],[3937,4145,"She and her lover planned it"],[4145,4229,"to get your money."]],"59":[[37,216,"It is no coincidence"],[216,408,"that you were saved that day."],[458,596,"The car accident"],[596,771,"was staged by her"],[771,921,"and her lover."],[921,1084,"The whole plan was to"],[1084,1255,"get your sympathy,"],[1255,1384,"get you to shower her"],[1384,1447,"with money,"],[1447,1522,"and then eventually"],[1522,1584,"marry her."],[1584,1722,"But that entire time"],[1722,1785,"that you two"],[1785,1881,"have been together,"],[1893,2003,"she's never"],[2003,2102,"lost touch with Jonathan."],[2160,2285,"She's lying."],[2285,2423,"She's making everything up."],[2460,2519,"You don't even need"],[2519,2615,"to take a DNA test"],[2615,2706,"because that child"],[2706,2798,"that she is carrying"],[2798,2936,"is not yours!"],[3103,3211,"It's her lover's,"],[3244,3332,"Jonathan."],[3374,3465,"And the original plan"],[3465,3611,"with all of that"],[3645,3728,"was to have her"],[3728,3924,"have your child"],[3924,4074,"and then murder you,"],[4074,4191,"so the child could inherit"],[4191,4325,"the Harper Corporation."],[4425,4491,"Mia,"],[4604,4825,"you plotted to kill my son?"],[5063,5213,"You make me sick, Mia."],[5301,5438,"Thank god I saw your act"],[5438,5597,"before it's too late."],[5597,5714,"Noah, no."],[5714,5839,"She's just jealous."],[5885,5964,"She's lying."],[5997,6076,"She's jealous"],[6076,6156,"because I'm"],[6156,6260,"the one"],[6260,6331,"that's going to marry you"],[6331,6439,"and have your baby."],[6439,6573,"It is not jealousy."],[6573,6677,"It is fact."],[6677,6835,"Look, I have proof."],[6835,6902,"Give it to me!"],[6902,6936,"No."]],"60":[[154,279,"That Harper boy"],[279,475,"is a total idiot..."],[600,678,"I had Jonathan"],[678,967,"drive right towards him,"],[967,1071,"and then I jumped"],[1071,1172,"right in front"],[1172,1322,"and acted like I saved him."],[1355,1522,"He totally bought it."],[1522,1597,"Jeez, Mia?"],[1597,1655,"I can't believe you"],[1655,1764,"pulled this off."],[1780,1918,"It was so easy."],[1918,2035,"Just a couple of tricks,"],[2035,2114,"now he's eating"],[2114,2231,"out of my hand."],[2565,2648,"And you know"],[2648,2727,"I'm pregnant."],[2727,2790,"Yeah."],[2790,2940,"It's Jonathan’s kid."],[3003,3186,"But that idiot Noah"],[3186,3340,"will have no clue."],[3415,3607,"And Jonathan's on board with this?"],[3674,3778,"Absolutely."],[3807,3953,"Once the baby's born,"],[4066,4145,"Noah just has to"],[4145,4287,"have a little accident."],[4354,4450,"And then,"],[4537,4629,"the Harper Fortune"],[4629,4788,"will be all ours."],[5976,6243,"You are disgusting,"],[6418,6552,"shameless,"],[6760,6894,"scheming,"],[7073,7198,"murderer!"],[7457,7549,"No!"],[7549,7699,"It's not what you think."],[7753,7836,"Vivian,"],[7836,7978,"Noah, please"],[7978,8066,"don't believe her."],[8066,8220,"That recording is fake."],[8220,8408,"That recording is 100% legit."],[8445,8533,"You have to trust me"],[8533,8621,"Mr. Harper."],[8654,8754,"How can he trust you?"],[8754,8900,"I'm the one he's marrying."],[8954,9088,"We'll get in touch with"],[9088,9334,"that lover of yours and see"],[9334,9526,"if he corroborates"],[9526,9642,"what Bella has said."],[9818,10035,"We’ll remove anyone."],[10039,10085,"You'll never"],[10085,10272,"set foot in L.A. again."]],"61":[[45,208,"We did nothing wrong."],[425,550,"To anyone"],[671,763,"who thinks"],[905,1009,"I won't have them"],[1009,1151,"kicked out of L.A."],[1330,1422,"Watch me."],[1614,1689,"Noah."],[2248,2431,"I want all Smith operations in L.A."],[2431,2506,"shut down."],[2615,2677,"Wipe them off"],[2677,2786,"the face of the earth."],[3361,3428,"Dad."],[3595,3653,"What?"],[3724,3862,"Our company went under?"],[3920,4037,"Uncle's too?"],[4421,4608,"Everything's ruined."],[4833,4917,"Mr. Harper."],[4938,5059,"All of you."],[5096,5167,"Please,"],[5167,5317,"please spare my family."],[5317,5413,"I promise"],[5463,5530,"the Smiths"],[5530,5684,"will cut ties"],[5684,5834,"with the Stone family"],[5901,5985,"right now."],[6039,6114,"Okay!"],[6210,6289,"Everybody."],[6352,6468,"One last chance."],[6585,6735,"Cut ties with the stones,"],[6752,6865,"you can leave right now."],[7090,7236,"But if it turns out that Mia's baby"],[7236,7340,"is not mine."],[7424,7515,"I promise to do more"],[7515,7582,"than just to kick you"],[7582,7657,"out of this city."],[7711,7766,"Oh, no."],[7766,7924,"Don't cut ties with us."],[7924,7982,"I'm..."],[7999,8179,"I am certain that Mia's baby"],[8179,8329,"is a Harper child."],[8562,8662,"It looks like even your friends"],[8662,8733,"don’t trust you."],[8846,8967,"Anything else to say, Mia?"]],"62":[[0,75,"Noah,"],[241,312,"you're the only"],[312,421,"man in my life."],[421,617,"I know I've made mistakes,"],[617,696,"but I've been"],[696,784,"taking care of you,"],[784,825,"making up"],[825,992,"for this whole time."],[1009,1146,"I haven't talked to Jonathan"],[1146,1259,"in forever."],[1334,1388,"Really?"],[1505,1605,"Then he probably misses you."],[1772,1897,"Mr. Harper,"],[2022,2118,"I want to show you"],[2118,2164,"a video"],[2164,2310,"that Jonathan sent me."],[2339,2431,"What video?"],[3257,3415,"Well,"],[3553,3674,"so I'm the father."],[3732,3924,"You don't believe me?"],[3941,4033,"Babe,"],[4087,4216,"I believe you."],[4300,4441,"What's the plan with Noah?"],[4533,4654,"Our kid"],[4683,4808,"is going to be"],[4808,4913,"the Harper heir."],[5030,5188,"I just have to get Noah"],[5188,5284,"out of the way."],[5284,5580,"And you will be a billionaire."],[5672,5805,"That's such a moron."],[5851,5880,"I don't know"],[5880,5989,"how they let a loser like that"],[5989,6110,"get so rich."],[6906,6981,"You've been lying to me"],[6981,7111,"for three goddamn years?"]],"63":[[29,141,"Noah, Noah."],[266,329,"Please,"],[329,450,"I haven't lied to you."],[471,638,"I don't even know Jonathan."],[688,792,"Bullshit."],[804,871,"Noah,"],[871,934,"he's the guy"],[934,996,"that you beat up"],[996,1067,"at the wedding."],[1121,1213,"Fuck you!"],[1330,1397,"Noah,"],[1422,1551,"I love you so much."],[1551,1743,"I can't live without you."],[2043,2152,"Mia, even now,"],[2152,2344,"you still can't admit it."],[2369,2502,"Vivian, I'm as confused"],[2502,2581,"as you are."],[2623,2765,"The recordings are fake."],[2777,2890,"Everything these people"],[2890,3048,"are saying is false."],[3048,3123,"I promise"],[3123,3282,"this baby is Noah's."],[3532,3699,"Bring the DNA results."],[3799,3903,"Yes, Mrs. Harper."],[4212,4350,"These DNA test results"],[4350,4433,"came back today."],[4542,4675,"They prove"],[4675,4750,"that the child"],[4750,4863,"that Mia's carrying"],[4896,5063,"is not Noah's."]],"64":[[50,187,"No. She's lying!"],[216,346,"The report is fake."],[446,550,"Get off me!"],[700,880,"You despicable"],[880,1001,"little whore."],[1138,1247,"I did not raise you"],[1247,1359,"to be like this."],[1534,1614,"Mr. Harper,"],[1680,1726,"please,"],[1826,1956,"give Mia another chance."],[2002,2106,"Take them away."],[2193,2423,"No, no, no,"],[2423,2640,"no, you can't do this to me."],[2648,2740,"No!"],[2806,2861,"And that goes"],[2861,2961,"for everyone else here"],[2961,3007,"as well."],[3036,3153,"You can either leave now"],[3174,3269,"or be taken away"],[3269,3378,"by the police like them."],[4158,4204,"I'm sorry,"],[4204,4254,"mom."],[4341,4416,"You fit this trip home"],[4416,4525,"into your busy schedule,"],[4525,4587,"and it just"],[4621,4767,"turned out to be a total mess."],[4950,5063,"I should have protected you."],[5242,5342,"Grandma."],[5380,5484,"It's my fault."],[5563,5651,"Let the Stones"],[5651,5739,"slip underneath the radar"],[5739,5780,"and..."],[5834,5943,"I spoiled your big day."],[6043,6131,"Don't be so hard"],[6131,6214,"on yourself."],[6335,6506,"Know that if this had not happened,"],[6506,6602,"we wouldn't have seen"],[6602,6760,"the Stone family's true colors."],[6848,7057,"I share the blame too."],[7090,7336,"I was just so obsessed"],[7336,7611,"to have a great grandchild."],[7699,7782,"Guys, I..."],[7907,8041,"I know we've been preoccupied"],[8041,8174,"lately with"],[8174,8362,"business matters, but"],[8487,8537,"I promise"],[8537,8629,"I'm going to pay more attention"],[8629,8742,"to the family in the future."],[8829,8917,"Well, it's too bad"],[8917,8979,"all the drama"],[8979,9038,"put a damper"],[9038,9154,"on the festivities."],[9184,9259,"It was going to be"],[9259,9388,"such a nice party."],[9430,9634,"Oh, it was fine."],[9718,9784,"Well,"],[9805,9889,"I did arrange"],[9889,9968,"a little surprise"],[9968,10122,"at a Michelin-star restaurant."],[10214,10347,"Supposed to go later, but,"],[10431,10485,"what the hell,"],[10485,10573,"let’s go now."],[10877,11002,"Wonderful."],[11073,11290,"I have such a good grandson"],[11336,11569,"and we'll be a family again."],[11603,11795,"Just the three of us."],[11899,12012,"You guys like spicy,"],[12012,12057,"right?"]]}